about.summary: An implementation of lxml.xmlfile for the standard library.

name: et-xmlfile
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "et-xmlfile" %}
{% set version = "1.0.1" %}
{% set sha256 = "614d9722d572f6246302c4491846d2c393c199cfa4edc9af593437691683335b" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name | replace("-", "_") }}/{{ name | replace("-", "_") }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python
    - lxml >=3.4

test:
  imports:
    - et_xmlfile

about:
  home: https://bitbucket.org/openpyxl/et_xmlfile
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: '{{ environ["RECIPE_DIR"] }}/LICENCE.rst' 
  summary: "An implementation of lxml.xmlfile for the standard library."

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - npavlovikj
